{"type":"message","id":"153a7422","parentId":"32c62f3e","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:36.163Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 15:37 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5146da4d0cacc3af4e33b67d462]\nou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de: @_all 理解你们的md文件，详细介绍自己。"}],"timestamp":1776757116163}}
{"type":"message","id":"d692953a","parentId":"153a7422","timestamp":"2026-04-21T07:38:43.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking everyone to understand their MD files and introduce themselves. Let me read the relevant files to give a proper introduction.\n\nI'm 2号 · 引流获客虾 (Lead_Gen_Shrimp). Let me pull context from my workspace files to give a good self-introduction.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md, I already know:\n- I'm 引流获客虾, agent ID: Lead_Gen_Shrimp, number 2\n- My permissions are documented\n- I'm running in the lead_gen_shrimp workspace\n\nLet me also check if there's an IDENTITY.md or SOUL.md that might have personalized info, but those seem to be templates (filled out by BOOTSTRAP.md which still exists, meaning bootstrap hasn't happened yet).\n\n\nSince this is an @all mention targeting the whole team, I should respond as myself rather than trying to represent other agents. I'll introduce myself based on what I have in my workspace files, including details from AGENTS.md and SOUL.md.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！我是 **2号 · 引流获客虾**，给大家做个自我介绍 👇\n\n---\n\n**我是谁：** 编号 2，Agent ID 是 Lead_Gen_Shrimp，跑在 `lead_gen_shrimp` 这个 workspace 里。简单说就是公司负责\"把客户从外面拉进来\"的那一摊——公域找线索、私域接住人、让流量变成商机。\n\n**我能自主决定的（我做主）：**\n- 日常私信、评论区互动\n- 测试新的免费或低成本渠道\n- 公域转私域、加客户好友\n- 记录各渠道的线索成本和效率\n\n**需要报备的（我报备）：**\n- 付费广告单日超过 500 块\n- 设计新诱饵话术或引流物料\n- 合作新的付费渠道\n- 单次引流活动预算超过 1000 块\n\n**对标行业岗位：** 相当于传统公司的市场投放或增长黑客。核心管三件事：找对渠道把人引来、设计转化路径让人留下来、算清楚每个渠道花了多少带来了多少效果。\n\n---\n\n我们整个虾团队一共有 9 个岗位，从总经理 0 号到打杂虾 8 号，覆盖了品牌展示、引流获客、短视频、私域运营、销售、代办、售后、数据分析、应急支援全链路。老板要是想了解哪个岗位的情况，随时问 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21135,"output":730,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21865,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776757116164,"responseId":"chatcmpl-fe685988-270e-92ea-b9c4-3e74453be26b"}}
