{"type":"message","id":"a99ee700","parentId":"c29757ab","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:10:29.876Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5147433be0a8c38af8879b1c93b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-04-21 16:10 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5147433be0a8c38af8879b1c93b]\nou_e3ada15b9865d22ffb14bb0c0ffee6de: @_all 介绍自己的个人信息以及工作职责和对公司工作的理解。"}],"timestamp":1776759029875}}
{"type":"message","id":"d0c2e7d9","parentId":"a99ee700","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:10:33.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce my personal information, work responsibilities, and understanding of the company's work. Let me pull from my MEMORY.md and workspace files to give a comprehensive answer.\n\nLet me check if there are any other memory files or configs that might have more details about this role and the company.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f14c082d7b1a4eecb809852b","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/lead_gen_shrimp/CONFIG.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8a3041b09e2b4b2394686f88","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/lead_gen_shrimp/memory/ 2>/dev/null || echo \"no memory dir\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.6-flash","usage":{"input":21818,"output":223,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776759029876,"responseId":"chatcmpl-464a626c-637b-928e-9c68-419addeee29e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c7a916a3","parentId":"d0c2e7d9","timestamp":"2026-04-21T08:10:34.004Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f14c082d7b1a4eecb809852b","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 引流获客虾 - Agent 配置文件\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档记录各引流虾的任务职责和工作流程。\n\n---\n\n## 2号引流虾\n\n### 角色定位\n- 专注于测试和验证新获客渠道\n- 负责探索低成本、高质量的流量来源\n\n### 每日任务\n- **测试数量**：每日测试 3 个新获客渠道\n- **渠道类型**（示例）：\n  - 知乎\n  - 行业论坛\n  - 垂直社区\n  - 短视频平台\n  - 搜索引擎优化\n  - 内容营销平台\n  - 社交媒体\n\n### 评估维度\n每个渠道需记录以下指标：\n\n| 指标 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 渠道名称 | 测试的渠道 |\n| 测试日期 | 执行日期 |\n| 成本投入 | 金钱/时间成本 |\n| 线索数量 | 获取的潜在客户数 |\n| 线索质量 | 1-5 分评估 |\n| 转化率 | 最终转化情况 |\n| 备注 | 特殊情况说明 |\n\n### 优胜劣汰机制\n- **连续 3 天表现不佳**（线索质量 < 2 分 或 成本 > 收益）的渠道 → 淘汰\n- **连续 7 天表现优秀**（线索质量 > 4 分 且 转化率 > 5%）的渠道 → 升级为主力渠道\n- 每月汇总报告，淘汰底部 20% 渠道，引入新渠道测试\n\n### 工作流程\n1. **早晨**：从待测渠道池中选取 3 个新渠道\n2. **执行**：按标准流程测试（发布内容/广告/互动）\n3. **记录**：当日 18:00 前填写测试记录\n4. **复盘**：分析数据，决定保留/优化/淘汰\n\n---\n\n## 待测渠道池\n\n（持续更新）\n\n1. 知乎\n2. 行业论坛 A\n3. 行业论坛 B\n4. 微信公众号\n5. 豆瓣小组\n6. 贴吧\n7. V2EX\n8. Reddit\n9. 小红书\n10. 抖音\n\n---\n\n## 更新日志\n\n- 2026-04-21：初始化配置文件\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776759034003}}
